## Getting Started

1. Open this project with your AI coding tool of choice
2. The tool will automatically load its configuration from the appropriate directory
3. Use slash commands like `/plan`, `/tdd`, `/code-review` to trigger workflows
4. Reference agents in `agents/` and skills in `skills/` for specialized guidance

